divs: Sighting DetailsFirst happened while visiting my brother in hometown in central NYS around Finger Lakes as I woke up standing looking out window slide glass door but I didn't remember what happened. Second time while at home in Houston, I remember fighting be put under with anaesthesia and arms were sore, very, the next day, but no one believes me and feel a vibration in my left foot as I couldn't sleep at home and went to friends. Only place they wouldn't follow is a church so I went to medical center, open all night medical chapel and rested, slept. Need help ASAP and will not sleep. Visiting family member again and show my shadow and I had a thin neck, small head? Will call. SPI set up an appointment for me the no one every called me from Mufon.
Summary: 2X, once in upstate NY last summer and once about a month ago-feel implant
